{"tid":919800,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【回饋顧客】翠華：年底前不加價 港人均消費約70至90元","createTime":"2018-11-28T10:27:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-28T13:37:56.000Z","uid":75969,"like":1,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f914e82c529811a52c55073d648968f827045d5e","tid":919800,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T10:27:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20181128/s00010/80378f8b048a5448206b373dd37ce800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20181128%2Fs00010%2F80378f8b048a5448206b373dd37ce800.jpg&h=db094152&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">楊東(右)、李遠康(中)、彭烱豪(左)(李紹昌攝)</span><br />\n<br />\n翠華（1314）公布中期業績，純利按年大減70%至1441萬元，行政總裁彭烱豪指出，受中美貿易戰影響，令人民幣匯率貶值，集團去年的匯兌收益達360萬元，不過今年上半財年就錄得800萬的虧損，未來會以多元化的方式發展，包括擴展業務至海外。<br />\n<br />\n翠華於一年之內合共開設5個新品牌，上半年就新增6間分店，4間為新品牌，另關閉2間翠華餐廳。彭烱豪表示，下半年已落實在內地及香港分別開設1間及3間店舖，首要會在未有分店的地區開店，例如上水、粉嶺。他又稱，集團每年約有六分之一的店舖需要續租，目前街舖租金有下調幅度，不過商場就持平。展望下個財年，翠華預料將會開設12間店舖，包括港澳、內地、海外及新品牌各個方面。<br />\n<br />\n翠華上半年香港的收入按年下跌4.9%至5.62億元，彭烱豪解釋，香港期內的同店銷售持平，遊客區的增長較大，至於內地的同店銷售就由去年的低單位數下滑，改善至平穩水平，相信業務會持續復甦。他又指，一般而言新品牌可在6個月達至收支平衡，集團其中一個品牌「廿一堂」就可收支平衡。<br />\n<br />\n目前翠華的香港人均消費約為70至90元，中國則界乎65至80元人民幣，主席李遠康表示，今年初稍為調整過早餐價格，現時未有計劃於今年底前調整餐單價格，以回饋顧客的支持。<br />\n<br />\n記者：蕭嘉聰<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1543396960060&amp;issue=20181128\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1543396960060%26issue%3D20181128&d=fPWMuOvQh280tnIgzO8zYkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=91c8b484\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1543396960060&amp;issue=20181128</a>"},{"pid":"f995960fe9866f513ea85c0ce1573bf639cdd06a","tid":919800,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T10:30:22.000Z","msg":"唔加價係因為無生意姐"},{"pid":"e1e3f50e3272d3e8043d087a421f254125e95273","tid":919800,"uid":35014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T10:33:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"92c1719c216d4a9c88ee2fd63d7171683b8bcdda","tid":919800,"uid":10757,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T10:35:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關港人事咩"},{"pid":"3df438badd81f30ead5446c60787505095213761","tid":919800,"uid":195009,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T10:41:14.000Z","msg":"愈黎愈垃圾 狗也不屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c8e4c81b1296d4bfd6e93a56a542cb2fab62230","tid":919800,"uid":104804,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T10:45:16.000Z","msg":"食大家樂好過佢"},{"pid":"adbc6fedc21ab0285e78c161ee59b90578455f7f","tid":919800,"uid":154505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T13:14:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食餐m記都好過佢"},{"pid":"0fcd82189020e073cfb1968d73f384953a02dc7f","tid":919800,"uid":80072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T13:18:49.000Z","msg":"咁貴又唔係特別占口質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee11613ff4fdf07921e9f249aeeefcdf6de0822c","tid":919800,"uid":133896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T13:24:34.000Z","msg":"啲質素差咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5094d3a2bf1dc21fb3a1589f6c5626a5fb5b695","tid":919800,"uid":11148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T13:28:35.000Z","msg":"70至90元呢個價位大把餐廳好食過翠華 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25c56e2b44a45b55194de46af6c68db50df9f086","tid":919800,"uid":178484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T13:29:00.000Z","msg":"年底前<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n過多兩日都12月喇喎。。。。"},{"pid":"3dc6ebdc3ca06f8ba28e0cc